07/Nov/22 10:47 AM;djagodzki;To complete this ticket and CI-7361
We will require custom script for posting record generator:
{code:java}
<entry key="postingRecordGeneration.ExpenseData.3">net.ifao.expense.logic.customSubActors.CustomScriptSubActor</entry>
  <entry key="postingRecordGeneration.ExpenseData.3.scriptContent">
      <![CDATA[
let postingRecords = element.getPostingRecords();
let travelSubPerdSum = element.getPriceLinkValue("TravelSubsistencePerDiemsSum").getAmount();
for (let i=0;i<postingRecords.size();i++){
  if(postingRecords.get(i).getDescription()==="Per-diems"){
    postingRecords.get(i).setAmount(travelSubPerdSum);
  }
}
]]>
  </entry> {code}
The script would take calculations from already present custom Amadeus per diem calculator and overwrite posing record value.
Incorrect values are a result of default posting record generator summing up absolute values of country sum links created via company rules.
The script overwrites summing up absolute values of country sum links and takes the value directly from custom Amadeus per diem calcultator, where the value is correctly calculated.

 ;;;

